The &#39;not canonicalized&#39; messages to STDERR are a bit of stray logging, 
originally meant to catch other problems, that should be harmless in the 
case of a recovery-log (or other action-directory-based) URI load.

I&#39;ll look into fixing it so they don&#39;t show up -- but in the meantime, 
don&#39;t worry about them. They&#39;re safe to ignore.

- Gordon @ IA

